  "original_title": "\u0dad\u0dd9\u0daf\u0dd2\u0db1\u0d9a\u0dca  \u0dad\u0dd4\u0dc5 \u0dc0\u0dd3 \u0d85\u0dbd\u0dd9\u0dc0\u0dd2 \u0db8\u0dab\u0dca\u0da9\u0dbd\u0dba \u0dc0\u0dd3 \u0db8\u0dd9\u0da7\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dca \u0da7\u0ddc\u0db1\u0dca 844\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db8\u0dd2\u0dbd \u0daf\u0dd3 \u0d9c\u0db1\u0dd3",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "In three days, the paddy marketing board buys 844 metric tons of paddy",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The farmers were in great difficulty because some rice millers bought the paddy harvest of the new season, which was grown in great difficulty by the farmers. Therefore, the Ministry of Agriculture started purchasing paddy through the Paddy Marketing Board.",
        "Currently, the price of one kilogram of paddy in the market has come down to 80-90 rupees.",
        "Therefore, measures were taken to buy rice from the farmers at a minimum price, and accordingly, the Paddy Marketing Board arranged to buy Nadu rice at 120 rupees, Samba rice at 125 rupees and Keeri samba rice at 130 rupees.",
        "This was approved by the Cabinet of Ministers and according to a request made by the Minister of Agriculture Mahinda Amaraweera, the government agreed to provide 2000 million rupees for the first phase of paddy purchase.",
        "Accordingly, in the last three days, 844,960 kg of paddy or 844 metric tons of paddy was able to be purchased, said Mr. Neil Alvis, the chairman of the board.",
        "The amount of paddy purchased yesterday (20) is 303 metric tons. 73 paddy warehouses in the districts where paddy has been harvested and are currently being harvested are still open today for purchasing paddy.",
        "Agriculture Minister Mahinda Amaraweera instructed the Paddy Marketing Board to continue purchasing rice at the government's minimum price."
      ],
